description: After being sidelined for three months due to an injury this season, Dragon has only done one match and is ready to be on the mat again! Dragon never missed a beat; if anything she came back stronger. Racking up a record 503 points and making Paris submit five times, the Dragon is back! Paris gets destroyed worse then any wrestler before her, ever! Can anyone stop the rampaging Dragon?
title: Part 2 of this weeks update. Dragon (1-0) vs: Paris (0-0)
